|eco=[[Chess/ECOC|C40]]
|parent=[[Chess/Latvian Gambit|Latvian Gambit]]
}}
= Latvian Gambit, Leonhardt Variation =
===4...fxe4===
Black threatens to play …d5 with beautiful development and only a slightly misplaced queen to worry about. But [[/5. Nc3/]] covers d5 and gains further time by hitting the e4-pawn. Rarely do such delicate works as Black's encounter such a robust spanner as 5. Nc3.



















{{ChessMid}}
