{{Documentation subpage}}
<!-- PLEASE ADD CATEGORIES AND INTERWIKIS AT THE BOTTOM OF THIS PAGE -->

Returns the namespace ID of page given, or of the current page.
{{Namespaces}}

=== Usage ===
* {{tlx|NAMESPACEID}} → {{NAMESPACEID}}
* {{tlx|NAMESPACEID|<nowiki></nowiki>}} → {{NAMESPACEID|}} <small>(''Main namespace'')</small>
* {{tlx|NAMESPACEID|<nowiki>{{ns:0}}</nowiki>}} → {{NAMESPACEID|{{ns:0}}}} <small>(''Main namespace'')</small>
* {{tlx|NAMESPACEID|Talk}} → {{NAMESPACEID|Talk}}

Namespace aliases are accepted, too:
* {{tlx|NAMESPACEID|Image}} → {{NAMESPACEID|Image}}
* {{tlx|NAMESPACEID|File}} → {{NAMESPACEID|File}}
* {{tlx|NAMESPACEID|WB}} → {{NAMESPACEID|WB}}
* {{tlx|NAMESPACEID|Project}} → {{NAMESPACEID|Project}}
* {{tlx|NAMESPACEID|Wikibooks}} → {{NAMESPACEID|Wikibooks}}

Invalid input returns an error, which can be caught with the [[mw:Help:Extension:ParserFunctions##iferror:|#iferror parser function]]:
* {{tlx|NAMESPACEID|Foo}} → {{NAMESPACEID|Foo}}

=== See also ===
* [[mw:Help:Magic words#Namespaces]]
* {{tl|ns has subpages}}
