==Parabola Function== * f(x) = x<sup>2</sup> : y = x<sup>2</sup> : x | -2 -1 0 1 2 : y | 4 -1 0 1 4
==Graph== :[[File:Qfunction.png|200px]] : A function y = x<sup>2</sup> has a parabola shape and passes through point (0,0)
